  "A climatologist collects temperature data at 50 weather stations and arranges them as vectors in R^50. She discovers that the data lies in a 3-dimensional subspace spanned by three weather patterns. She wants to express today's temperature as coordinates in this basis. What does the coordinate vector look like?": "",
